quests.desc: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First of all, you could, like, open the rectangular safe. Then, retrieve the cuboid key from the rectangular safe within the workshop. With the cuboid key, assure that the cuboid safe is unlocked with the cuboid key. And then, ensure that the cuboid safe is open. And then, take the Microsoft key from the cuboid safe. And then, insert the Microsoft key into the Microsoft locker's lock to unlock it. After that, ensure that the Microsoft locker in the workshop is open. After opening the Microsoft locker, take the sandwich from the Microsoft locker in the workshop. And then, head east. And then, deposit the sandwich on the floor of the canteen. Got that? Good!

objective: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First, it would be great if you could open the rectangular safe inside the workshop. And then, take the cuboid key from the rectangular safe in the workshop. With the cuboid key, check that the cuboid safe inside the workshop is unlocked with the cuboid key. Then, ensure that the cuboid safe is open. If you have opened the cuboid safe, retrieve the Microsoft key from the cuboid safe within the workshop. And then, assure that the Microsoft locker in the workshop is unlocked. And then, open the Microsoft locker inside the workshop. Then, recover the sandwich from the Microsoft locker inside the workshop. Then, move east. Then, drop the sandwich on the floor of the canteen. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
